data.description: Experience the warmth of home in this remarkable residence! Nestled in the sought-after Kingdom Heights neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 3 1/2-bath home boasts a game room and ample space for hosting guests. The open-concept design is flooded with natural light through numerous windows. The backyard features a patio, providing a perfect spot to relax and take in the breathtaking Texas sunsets. Don't miss the chance to tour this exquisite home before it's off the market!
